# Claude Context System
# Recommended .gitignore patterns for projects using the system

# Personal configuration (optional - uncomment if you want to keep config private)
# context/.context-config.json

# Generated artifacts (optional - uncomment if you don't want to track these)
# artifacts/
# artifacts/code-reviews/
# artifacts/lighthouse/
# artifacts/performance/
# artifacts/security/
# artifacts/bundle-analysis/
# artifacts/coverage/

# Context documentation (usually tracked, but can be excluded for team projects)
# context/
# context/CLAUDE.md
# context/SESSIONS.md

# Note: By default, the Claude Context System tracks all files.
# This allows perfect session continuity and documentation preservation.
#
# Uncomment sections above based on your needs:
# - Solo project: Track everything (leave commented)
# - Team project: Exclude context/ if each dev has their own preferences
# - CI/CD project: Exclude artifacts/ if they're regenerated
